      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to see the point of any of this lately. like, we're just tiny specks on a rock that's eventually going to be swallowed by the sun, and then even the sun dies. everything we do, every struggle, every feeling... it just disappears into nothing. it feels like we're all just playing a game that's rigged to end in total silence, so why even bother trying to win?",
